    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine mechanical and cosmetic condition. This example is powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. The valvetrain is exceptionally quiet, with a fully documented VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement already completed for long-term structural integrity. Power is channeled through a precise Getrag six-speed manual transmission and a factory-calibrated M-Variable limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry is flawless, maintaining the communicative feedback and lateral grip this chassis is celebrated for. With zero oxidation and an immaculate cabin, this M3 represents the pinnacle of analog driving dynamics.",
